    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:14:25.056+09:00">“If you fail to win by words,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:14:38.294+09:00">do not resort to your thoughts;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:14:46.584+09:00">if you fail to win by your thoughts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:14:56.09+09:00">do not resort to your vital energy."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:15:40.64+09:00">It is right not to resort to your vital energy, when you fail to win by thoughts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:16:32.741+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:16:37.795+09:00">but it is wrong not to resort to your vital energy when you fail to win by words.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:16:57.747+09:00">The will is commander over the vital energy</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:17:08.19+09:00">and vital energy is what fills the body.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:18:51.324+09:00">The vital energy manifests itself</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T19:21:52.158+09:00">wherever the will goes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:46:41.699+09:00">What do you mean by analyzing others' speech?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:50:54.07+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:51:03.273+09:00">"If the speech is not impartial I can see where lies the speaker's  lopsided view;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:51:11.828+09:00">If it is exaggerated I can see where he looses his footing.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:51:39.63+09:00">If it is deviant I can see where he goes astray.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:52:21.281+09:00">If it is evasive I can see where he is unjustifiable.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:52:52.017+09:00">those four kinds of speech are all expressionsof the mind,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:53:10.245+09:00">which will surely affect politics unfavorably.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:52:01.839+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-22a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:54:03.067+09:00">A sage</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-23a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-16T06:54:09.823+09:00">would no doubt agree with me."</seg>
                </p>
